Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…他？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公元2307年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自Celestial Being開始武力干預以來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4個月的時間即將過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的干預行動超過了60次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管人們是否願意  都在逐漸接受他們的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是Celestial Being的反對者還是支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在反對戰爭方面都是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不希望有戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上的三個國家群中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合和AEU僅在同盟國內的紛爭事變方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發表了針對Celestial Being的防禦行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自從莫拉里亞紛爭以來卻未曾出現過一次大規模的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以會有這種事  是因為MS Gundam的卓越戰鬥能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界範圍內出現的紛爭在不斷縮小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對於武力壓制的反對卻並未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  在唯一以對決姿態面對他們的人類革新聯盟中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個極秘作戰計劃即將展開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:23.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}#09  大國的威信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特務部隊  頂武隊員的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位既是本國的代表  也是人類革新聯盟的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:28.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}人革聯  高軌道平台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位的任務是剿滅在世界範圍內持續著武力干預的武裝組織
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並奪取MS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能完成這一任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們人類革新聯盟將引領世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並對人類的發展作出巨大貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望各位抖擻精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  著艦完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面進入Exia的著艦作業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸器打開  相對誘導系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘導系統  同步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  現在著艦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  著艦完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著艦得不錯哦  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫忙進行整備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回房間休息去吧  別搶別人的飯碗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥  哥哥  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感動的會面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始整備  開始整備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  若在大修中遇上敵襲該如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨老天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是戰術預報員的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姿態控制完成  艙門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線性彈射器電壓上升
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙向通訊系統  發射準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊子機  整體分離
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊子機開始整體分離  正在向預定位置移動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:41.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,0)}人革聯  高軌道平台管制室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙向通訊正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  我軍的靜止衛星軌道區域已覆蓋了80%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam放射出的特殊粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有干擾效果範圍內的通訊設備的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反其道而行之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過進行雙向通訊  釋放出幾十萬的小型探測裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則在有無法通訊的區域時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是表明有Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  魚兒會上鉤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不是這樣可就不好辦了  明副官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入如此大量物資的作戰計劃並非隨便要進行幾次都可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Celestial Being的動向下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界紛爭今後的狀況…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩的論文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西  隨便寫寫不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你啊  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是在航行管制嗎  為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了代議員老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次和你提起過吧  我的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫沙慈  沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  女兒給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也該夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  回去吧  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界現在這種狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓女孩子家一個人在外留學呢  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛  我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說點什麼啊  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人要被帶走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…您誤會了  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是  我不是這意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男孩子的話就乾脆點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對伊奧利亞·修亨伯格的調查報道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若對Celestial Being的創始人進行調查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該就能知道他們的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說無論哪個國家的諜報機關都毫無辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人能怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也想做  拜託你了  主任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在1月內收集到1分鐘的報道特輯題材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一則新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}聯合國對能量枯竭狀況日益加劇的中東王國阿扎提斯坦進行了援助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:15.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}阿扎提斯坦王國\N阿扎提斯坦王國國際機場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國的視察團已經抵達當地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能和聯合國大使談得攏  那太陽光發電系統也會對本國…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  好像到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位會拯救阿扎提斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聯合國大使  亞歷桑德羅·柯納
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿扎提斯坦王國第一公主  瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能接受我們的援助請求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我謹代表我國表示謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國原本就是為此而成立的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  如今加盟國滯納分擔費用  能辦到的事十分有限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  還是要謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國在這種時候的援助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒什麼東西能夠抵押
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男的  在想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  菲露特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是身體不適  到莫雷諾那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指值班人連小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊交給我  你去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真的嗎  好體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  不是我喜歡的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太融洽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN驅動器填充  到達100%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AE3288的雙向通訊中斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向中校彙報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AR9763也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置是EAN07
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會是這麼近…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向特務部隊  頂武的全體成員傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊  緊急出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}人革聯  多用途運輸艦  拉奧和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自0655  從1號艦起依次出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全搭乘人員加速準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在140秒後開始緊急加速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲少尉  全感覺投影系統狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題  中校  一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對少尉而言可是首次實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不希望發生上次那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦達到可加速區域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  菲露特的父母曾在Celestial Being待過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說兩人都是第二代的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是託你父母的福才戰鬥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是想家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是兩人的祭日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  只知道是過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的成員有保密的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚當前成員的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  連雙親的消息也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你繼承了雙親的遺志呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很堅強  是個堅強的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼爾  我原名叫尼爾·迪蘭地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出身於愛爾蘭  雙親死於恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是由你說  不太公平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅限於對女性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那種狀況下  能嘗出什麼味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E傳感器有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…通訊裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人探測到了我們的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變托勒密的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以最短距離朝軌道環前進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各Meister在Gundam待機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  Gundam的整備狀況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia整備好了  但Dynames的腳部發電機還無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲也處於拆除狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Kyrios  Virtue先出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  轉為彈射模式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然通過散佈幾十萬的通訊裝置來確定GN粒子的通訊遮斷區域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能採用這種大量物資作戰計劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是人革…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟  無法突破敵方通訊區域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝軌道環的發電衛星前進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於電磁波的影響  那裡為無通訊地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若狀況能維持5分鐘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios已出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使Virtue轉移至彈射甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想以兩台Gundam進行佯攻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有此意…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  出擊順序拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過應急處理在左腳上裝上了固定用具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但武器管制的調節…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能射擊就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:13:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue  特瑞亞·埃德  出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  朝軌道環前進的通訊遮斷點又增加了兩處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam分散了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是讓兩台Gundam出擊的佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是這樣  那處於第一通訊遮斷點的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就是Celestial Being的宇宙運輸艦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就以牙還牙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號艦到3號艦  MS全體出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號  3號的掌舵員  切換成自動掌舵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艦橋分離後  返回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號艦  別忘了跟蹤第3通訊遮斷點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號艦到3號艦  MS全體出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照預定  在1號艦後方形成縱列隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號、3號艦  艦橋脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號艦  開始跟蹤第3通訊遮斷點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號艦  跟蹤第2通訊遮斷點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入軌道變更
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本隊以1號艦為主軸  追蹤第1通訊遮斷點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標推測是敵運輸艦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能捕捉到  進入作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  已進入軌道環的電磁波干涉區域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學攝影機捕捉到敵方部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大望遠距離  在顯示屏上顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近的艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類革新聯盟軍的多用途運輸艦EDI402拉奧和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷定有四艘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩艘分別在左右散開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是去攻擊Kyrios和Virtue
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向阿里路亞他們的通訊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處於電磁波干涉區域  這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特  馬上改變軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以軌道環作為掩護  與敵艦保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:15:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦改變軌道  隱藏到了軌道環的陰影中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能顯示敵艦的艦影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用AI進行過了修正
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Celestial Being的宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說那個組織的規模大到連這種東西都有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全體成員傳達戰術分析員的狀況預測
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近的艦船有兩艘運輸艦——拉奧和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計敵方所有的戰力都集中在了那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩艘敵艦應該去迎擊Kyrios和Virtue了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來不希望那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希望看穿我們佯攻的敵方艦隊會忽略阿里路亞他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而直接朝我們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那樣  那就能像預定那樣繞到敵軍後方來進行夾擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人以佯攻來應對我們的佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前去攻擊的敵方運輸艦上所搭載的MS恐怕已全部出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反  \N阿里路亞和特瑞亞估計正在迎擊運輸艦  從而耗費了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真費工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有搭載MS？  不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭遇敵人佯攻的阿里路亞他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估計會在6分鐘後回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其間  我們將受到敵方MS部隊的波浪式進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  你這麼預測的根據是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18年前  在第4次太陽光紛爭時採用了與此相同的作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革聯的作戰指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是俄羅斯的外號叫作「暴熊」的謝爾蓋·斯密爾諾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本隊的作戰開始時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要浪費生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  Dynames  運輸器艙門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia在普特利麥奧斯的前方以迎擊形態待機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  將腳部固定在運輸器上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GN來福槍以迎擊射擊狀態待機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將托勒密的優先權轉為防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斷常規電源
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的要開戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船明明沒有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有Gundam在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只有兩台嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  敵方該出擊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持360秒試試
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方運輸艦從環的陰影中出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  開始炮擊阻擊戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於機體重量的變化  瞄準偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅修正  哈羅修正
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了  用手動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有導彈靠近  數量為24
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN場展開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種速度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是用無人艦採取的特攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特  特攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓你們得逞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN場再次展開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜·西爾納
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員…要活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特說得沒錯  我們要活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何  都要堅持下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已確認敵方MS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在了運輸艦的後方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方總數為36台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛張聲勢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入了死角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦橋  轉一下運輸器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在引誘我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果上前  那防禦便會變得薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方姿態不確定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是這種程度的攻擊的話  那可以用GN場來應付
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微  稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有悖MS的艦船攻擊理論的遠距離攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這麼回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革聯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  謝爾蓋·斯密爾諾夫此次的作戰目的並不是托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是捕獲Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說我的預測失算了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明決定不會再搞錯了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼了  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械雷部隊  被誘導了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才這種程度  Kyrios會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  這種像刺中了頭部一樣的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那時一樣的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是什麼  到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識你！
